title: My Famous Babysitter
overview: In each episode of My Famous Babysitter, a celebrity steps up to parent demanding kids as their parents enjoy some well-earned rest and relaxation.With a chaperone and a psychologist monitoring their every move, the celebs face uphill battles with discipline, homework and arguments over bedtime. At the end of their time in charge they face some honest feedback from the parents and the kids, and it proves to be an emotional experience for everyone involved.
